casebody.data:
BROWNE, Appellant, v. BAKER et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 15, 1893.) Action by Mary A. Browne against John M. Baker and another, as administrators.

Argued before O’BRIEN and PARKER, JJ.

A. N. Card, for appellant. W. E. Stiger, for respondents.

No opinion. Upon payment of $10 costs to defendant, motion to dismiss denied.
